column1: 📨 As hurricanes and COVID-19 continue to be a danger in Florida voting by mail is the safest way to vote this election. You can mail it back drop it off at a secure drop box during Early Vote or bring it to a Supervisor of Elections office. Learn more: https://t.co/5uaCgDTlXP

@ValDemings is the best choice for #VP as a woman of color and a former police chief with a proven record of level-headed leadership amidst crises — much needed as we battle racial injustice and the health and economic devastation of COVID-19. ✅ #ValforVP #BidenDemings
